actors, the FINAL RANK shall be calculated.</p><br> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">The FINAL RANK  shall be a combination of (a) and (b), where (a) being the value of knowledge and/or skill shall hold more value than (b). </p> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">The user shall get a chance to play the game 3 times on one ticket, and the average of all the 3 PERFORMANCE SCORES shall be considered for all the players.</p>'),(4344,216,'_save_the_bunny_description','field_5f0c17ff287a0'),(4345,216,'bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_one',''),(4346,216,'_bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_one','field_5f0c184d402e5'),(4347,216,'bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_two',''),(4348,216,'_bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_two','field_5f0ec2adc2b94'),(4349,216,'bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_three',''),(4350,216,'_bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_three','field_5f0ec2bbc2b97'),(4351,216,'bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_one',''),(4352,216,'_bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_one','field_5f0c184d402e5'),(4353,216,'bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_two',''),(4354,216,'_bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_two','field_5f0ec2adc2b94'),(4355,216,'bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_three',''),(4356,216,'_bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_three','field_5f0ec2bbc2b97'),(4357,216,'bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_one',''),(4358,216,'_bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_one','field_5f0c184d402e5'),(4359,216,'bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_two',''),(4360,216,'_bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_two','field_5f0ec2adc2b94'),(4361,216,'bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_three',''),(4362,216,'_bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_three','field_5f0ec2bbc2b97'),(4363,216,'bunny_table_data_3_tr_data_one',''),(4364,216,'_bunny_table_data_3_tr_data_one','field_5f0c184d402e5'),(4365,216,'bunny_table_data_3_tr_data_two',''),(4366,216,'_bunny_table_data_3_tr_data_two','field_5f0ec2adc2b94'),(4367,216,'bunny_table_data_3_tr_data_three',''),(4368,216,'_bunny_table_data_3_tr_data_three','field_5f0ec2bbc2b97'),(4369,216,'bunny_table_data_4_tr_data_one',''),(4370,216