 be calculated.</p><br> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">The FINAL RANK  shall be a combination of (a) and (b), where (a) being the value of knowledge and/or skill shall hold more value than (b). </p> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">The user shall get a chance to play the game 3 times on one ticket, and the average of all the 3 PERFORMANCE SCORES shall be considered for all the players.</p>'),(5008,226,'_save_the_bunny_description','field_5f0c17ff287a0'),(5009,226,'bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_one',''),(5010,226,'_bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_one','field_5f0c184d402e5'),(5011,226,'bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_two',''),(5012,226,'_bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_two','field_5f0ec2adc2b94'),(5013,226,'bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_three',''),(5014,226,'_bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_three','field_5f0ec2bbc2b97'),(5015,226,'bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_one',''),(5016,226,'_bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_one','field_5f0c184d402e5'),(5017,226,'bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_two',''),(5018,226,'_bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_two','field_5f0ec2adc2b94'),(5019,226,'bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_three',''),(5020,226,'_bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_three','field_5f0ec2bbc2b97'),(5021,226,'bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_one',''),(5022,226,'_bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_one','field_5f0c184d402e5'),(5023,226,'bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_two',''),(5024,226,'_bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_two','field_5f0ec2adc2b94'),(5025,226,'bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_three',''),(5026,226,'_bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_three','field_5f0ec2bbc2b97'),(5027,226,'bunny_table_data_3_tr_data_one',''),(5028,226,'_bunny_table_data_3_tr_data_one','field_5f0c184d402e5'),(5029,226,'bunny_table_data_3_tr_data_two',''),(5030,226,'_bunny_table_data_3_tr_data_two','field_5f0ec2adc2b94'),(5031,226,'bunny_table_data_3_tr_data_three',''),(5032,226,'_bunny_table_data_3_tr_data_three','field_5f0ec2bbc2b97'),(5033,226,'bunny_table_data_4_tr_data_one',''),(5034,226,'_bunny_table_data_4_tr_dat