nce to play the game 3 times on one ticket, and the average of all the 3 PERFORMANCE SCORES shall be considered for all the players.</p>'),(5578,235,'_save_the_bunny_description','field_5f0c17ff287a0'),(5579,235,'bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_one',''),(5580,235,'_bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_one','field_5f0c184d402e5'),(5581,235,'bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_two',''),(5582,235,'_bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_two','field_5f0ec2adc2b94'),(5583,235,'bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_three',''),(5584,235,'_bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_three','field_5f0ec2bbc2b97'),(5585,235,'bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_one',''),(5586,235,'_bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_one','field_5f0c184d402e5'),(5587,235,'bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_two',''),(5588,235,'_bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_two','field_5f0ec2adc2b94'),(5589,235,'bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_three',''),(5590,235,'_bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_three','field_5f0ec2bbc2b97'),(5591,235,'bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_one',''),(5592,235,'_bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_one','field_5f0c184d402e5'),(5593,235,'bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_two',''),(5594,235,'_bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_two','field_5f0ec2adc2b94'),(5595,235,'bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_three',''),(5596,235,'_bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_three','field_5f0ec2bbc2b97'),(5597,235,'bunny_table_data_3_tr_data_one',''),(5598,235,'_bunny_table_data_3_tr_data_one','field_5f0c184d402e5'),(5599,235,'bunny_table_data_3_tr_data_two',''),(5600,235,'_bunny_table_data_3_tr_data_two','field_5f0ec2adc2b94'),(5601,235,'bunny_table_data_3_tr_data_three',''),(5602,235,'_bunny_table_data_3_tr_data_three','field_5f0ec2bbc2b97'),(5603,235,'bunny_table_data_4_tr_data_one',''),(5604,235,'_bunny_table_data_4_tr_data_one','field_5f0c184d402e5'),(5605,235,'bunny_table_data_4_tr_data_two',''),(5606,235,'_bunny_table_data_4_tr_data_two','field_5f0ec2adc2b94'),(5607,235,'bunny_table_data_4_tr_data_three',''),(5608,235,'_bunny_table_data_4_tr_data_three','field_5f0ec2bbc2b97'),(5609,235,'bunny_table_data_5_tr_data_one',''),(5610,235,'_bunny_tab