e achieved purely due to the performance of knowledge and/or skill.</p><br> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">b) TIME COUNT: The amount of time taken to complete that particular contest. The time shall be measured in terms of milliseconds, i.e., represented as  XX:YY:ZZZ (where \'X\' is minutes, and \'Y\' is seconds, and \'Z\' is millisecond). 			There will be no embedded time limit for this; however, the player has to take care to complete the game within the window time of the contest.</p><br> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">After calculating both the factors, the FINAL RANK shall be calculated.</p><br> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">The FINAL RANK  shall be a combination of (a) and (b), where (a) being the value of knowledge and/or skill shall hold more value than (b).</p> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">The user shall get a chance to play the game 3 times on one ticket, and the average of all the 3 PERFORMANCE SCORES shall be considered for all the players.</p>'),(6130,244,'__brick_game_description','field_5f0eda6c0a5ec'),(6131,244,'brick_table_row_data_0_tr_data_one','FINAL SCORE'),(6132,244,'_brick_table_row_data_0_tr_data_one','field_5f0edab80a5ef'),(6133,244,'brick_table_row_data_0_tr_data_two','522 points'),(6134,244,'_brick_table_row_data_0_tr_data_two','field_5f0edab80a5f0'),(6135,244,'brick_table_row_data_0_tr_data_three','522 points'),(6136,244,'_brick_table_row_data_0_tr_data_three','field_5f0edab80a5f1'),(6137,244,'brick_table_row_data_0_tr_data_four','522 points'),(6138,244,'_brick_table_row_data_0_tr_data_four','field_5f0edab80a5f2'),(6139,244,'brick_table_row_data_1_tr_data_one','FINAL RANKING'),(6140,244,'_brick_table_row_data_1_tr_data_one','field_5f0edab80a5ef'),(6141,244,'brick_table_row_data_1_tr_data_two','3'),(6142,244,'_brick_table_row_data_1_tr_data_two','field_5f0edab80a5f0'),(6143,244,'brick_t