ass=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">b) TIME COUNT: The amount of time taken to complete that particular contest. The time shall be measured in terms of milliseconds, i.e., represented as  XX:YY:ZZZ (where \'X\' is minutes, and \'Y\' is seconds, and \'Z\' is millisecond). 			There will be no embedded time limit for this; however, the player has to take care to complete the game within the window time of the contest.</p><br> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">After calculating both the factors, the FINAL RANK shall be calculated.</p><br> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">The FINAL RANK  shall be a combination of (a) and (b), where (a) being the value of knowledge and/or skill shall hold more value than (b). </p> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">The user shall get a chance to play the game 3 times on one ticket, and the average of all the 3 PERFORMANCE SCORES shall be considered for all the players.</p>'),(7452,265,'_save_the_bunny_description','field_5f0c17ff287a0'),(7453,265,'bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_one',''),(7454,265,'_bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_one','field_5f0c184d402e5'),(7455,265,'bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_two',''),(7456,265,'_bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_two','field_5f0ec2adc2b94'),(7457,265,'bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_three',''),(7458,265,'_bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_three','field_5f0ec2bbc2b97'),(7459,265,'bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_one',''),(7460,265,'_bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_one','field_5f0c184d402e5'),(7461,265,'bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_two',''),(7466,266,'banner_slider_0_image','62'),(7467,266,'_banner_slider_0_image','field_5f04fc666fad3'),(7468,266,'banner_slider','3'),(7469,266,'_banner_slider','field_5f04fc596fad2'),(7470,266,'zone','4'),(7471,266,'_zone','field_5f04fe3d71000'),(7472,266,'how_to_play_description','First of all, you have to pick up a category according to your choice. Thereafter, you can join the conte