8152,267,'brick_game_description','<h2 class=\"main_heading\"> RANKING & SCORING SYSTEMS FOR ‘THE BRICK GAME’</h2> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">It’s a game where you have to create horizontal/vertical grid lines of bricks to earn scores. The FINAL RANKING of every contest for all the users is based on two parameters:</p> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">a) PERFORMANCE  SCORE: The score achieved purely due to the performance of knowledge and/or skill.</p><br> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">b) TIME COUNT: The amount of time taken to complete that particular contest. The time shall be measured in terms of milliseconds, i.e., represented as  XX:YY:ZZZ (where \'X\' is minutes, and \'Y\' is seconds, and \'Z\' is millisecond). 			There will be no embedded time limit for this; however, the player has to take care to complete the game within the window time of the contest.</p><br> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">After calculating both the factors, the FINAL RANK shall be calculated.</p><br> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">The FINAL RANK  shall be a combination of (a) and (b), where (a) being the value of knowledge and/or skill shall hold more value than (b).</p> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">The user shall get a chance to play the game 3 times on one ticket, and the average of all the 3 PERFORMANCE SCORES shall be considered for all the players.</p>'),(8153,267,'general_rule_description','<p class=\"title\">GENERAL RULES IN CASE OF TIE SITUATION</p> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">*  All rules and conditions mentioned here are blanket rules and applicable to all users in all the contests (quiz and games) in equal aspects whatsoever, without any bias or preferences of any kind.</p><br>  			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">In the case of a tie among some of the players, a total sum of all the rewards of those particular players is computed. After that, the average amount is calculated, and equal amounts of money is distributed among all the respective players. Below are different scenarios for the cases of tie:</p><br>'),(8154,267,'_general_rule_description','field_5f0ee5c7e151a'),(8155,267,'condition_table_0_title','Condition in e.g. 1 : '),(8156,267,'_condition_table_0_title','field_5f0ee69b1e75d'),(8157,267,'condition_table_0_description_one','There are 3 players out of 10 players in set 1 who are a tie.<br> 			Hence, Spot nos. 3, 4 & 5 have been occupied by rank 3 (refer fig 3 for illustration)'),(8158,267,'_condition_table_0_description_one','field_5f0ee6a21e75e'),(8159,267,'condition_table_0_description_two','Here, the total amount of spot 3,4, & 5 i.e. 100+100+100= Rs.300 will be equally distributed to all rankers – i.e.  Rs. 300/3'),(8160,267,'_condition_table_0_description_two','field_5f0ee6ae1e75f'),(8161,267,'condition_table_0_condition_table_row_data_0_tr_data_one','FINAL SCORE'),(8162,267,'_condition_table_0_condition_table_row_data_0_tr_data_one','field_5f0ee6d41e762'),(8163,267,'condition_table_0_condition_table_row_data_0_tr_data_two','522 points'),(8164,267,'_condition_table_0_condition_table_row_data_0_tr_data_two','field_5f0ee6d41e763'),(8165,267,'condition_table_0_condition_table_row_data_0_tr_data_three','522 points'),(8166,267,'_condition_table_0_condition_table_row_data_0_tr_data_three','field_5f0ee6d41e764'),(8167,267,'condition_table_0_condition_table_row_data_0_tr_data_four','522 points'),(8168,267,'_condition_table_0_condition_table_row_data_0_tr_data_four','field_5f0ee6d41e765'),(8169,267,'condition_table_0_condition_table_row_data_1_tr_data_one','FINAL RANKING'),(8170,267,'_condition_table_0_condition_table_row_data_1_tr_data_one','field_5f0ee6d41e762'),(8171,267,'condition_table_0_condition_table_row_data_1_tr_data_t