particular contest. The time shall be measured in terms of milliseconds, i.e., represented as  XX:YY:ZZZ (where \'X\' is minutes, and \'Y\' is seconds, and \'Z\' is millisecond). 			There will be no embedded time limit for this; however, the player has to take care to complete the game within the window time of the contest.</p><br> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">After calculating both the factors, the FINAL RANK shall be calculated.</p><br> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">The FINAL RANK  shall be a combination of (a) and (b), where (a) being the value of knowledge and/or skill shall hold more value than (b). </p> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">The user shall get a chance to play the game 3 times on one ticket, and the average of all the 3 PERFORMANCE SCORES shall be considered for all the players.</p>'),(8455,268,'_save_the_bunny_description','field_5f0c17ff287a0'),(8456,268,'bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_one',''),(8457,268,'_bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_one','field_5f0c184d402e5'),(8458,268,'bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_two',''),(8459,268,'_bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_two','field_5f0ec2adc2b94'),(8460,268,'bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_three',''),(8461,268,'_bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_three','field_5f0ec2bbc2b97'),(8462,268,'bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_one',''),(8463,268,'_bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_one','field_5f0c184d402e5'),(8464,268,'bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_two',''),(8465,268,'_bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_two','field_5f0ec2adc2b94'),(8466,268,'bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_three',''),(8467,268,'_bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_three','field_5f0ec2bbc2b97'),(8468,268,'bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_one',''),(8469,268,'_bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_one','field_5f0c184d402e5'),(8470,268,'bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_two',''),(8471,268,'_bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_two','field_5f0ec2adc2b94'),(8472,268,'bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_three',''),(8473,268,'_bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_t