cond). 			There will be no embedded time limit for this; however, the player has to take care to complete the game within the window time of the contest.</p><br> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">After calculating both the factors, the FINAL RANK shall be calculated.</p><br> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">The FINAL RANK  shall be a combination of (a) and (b), where (a) being the value of knowledge and/or skill shall hold more value than (b). </p> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">The user shall get a chance to play the game 3 times on one ticket, and the average of all the 3 PERFORMANCE SCORES shall be considered for all the players.</p>'),(9541,271,'_save_the_bunny_description','field_5f0c17ff287a0'),(9542,271,'bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_one',''),(9543,271,'_bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_one','field_5f0c184d402e5'),(9544,271,'bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_two',''),(9545,271,'_bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_two','field_5f0ec2adc2b94'),(9546,271,'bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_three',''),(9547,271,'_bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_three','field_5f0ec2bbc2b97'),(9548,271,'bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_one',''),(9549,271,'_bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_one','field_5f0c184d402e5'),(9550,271,'bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_two',''),(9551,271,'_bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_two','field_5f0ec2adc2b94'),(9552,271,'bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_three',''),(9553,271,'_bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_three','field_5f0ec2bbc2b97'),(9554,271,'bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_one',''),(9555,271,'_bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_one','field_5f0c184d402e5'),(9556,271,'bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_two',''),(9557,271,'_bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_two','field_5f0ec2adc2b94'),(9558,271,'bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_three',''),(9559,271,'_bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_three','field_5f0ec2bbc2b97'),(9560,271,'bunny_table_data_3_tr_data_one',''),(9561,271,'_bunny_table_data_3_tr_data_one','field_5f0c184d402e5'),(9562,271,'bunny_table_data_3