ld_5f04fffe95c4a'),(11682,287,'consecutive_score_system_score_list','5'),(11683,287,'_consecutive_score_system_score_list','field_5f05002495c4b'),(11684,287,'consecutive_score_system',''),(11685,287,'_consecutive_score_system','field_5f04fff195c49'),(11686,287,'features_description','An app is always defined by its features and specifics. MILLIONTREE has four basic peculiarities which make it unique. These characteristics are portrayed by our provision of equality to all the players, reflection of transparency, availability of fair play and a firm trust base. '),(11687,287,'_features_description','field_5f0500920be82'),(11688,287,'features_boxes','4'),(11689,287,'_features_boxes','field_5f0500d60be83'),(11690,287,'features',''),(11691,287,'_features','field_5f0500810be81'),(11692,287,'faq','13'),(11693,287,'_faq','field_5f050635af48a'),(11694,287,'about_us_description','MILLIONTREE is India\'s first & most trusted platform crafted exclusively for earning money on the grounds of knowledge & skill. Remember, luck isn\'t a deciding factor here.  Showcase your brainpower and win real money at nominal ticket costs. With that being said, we would also like to mention the core brand values of MILLIONTREE:'),(11695,287,'_about_us_description','field_5f05068d916c7'),(11696,287,'about_us_feature_list','8'),(11697,287,'_about_us_feature_list','field_5f050698916c8'),(11698,287,'about_us_information','We strongly believe that we should also contribute to the societal goals for the overall betterment of the nation. This notion has inspired us to do our bit for the welfare of farmers and Indian defense forces in the form of our CSR activities. </p>         <p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"fade-up\" data-aos-duration=\"2000\">All in all now is the time for you to grab the golden chance to win prizes at minimal prices. Just choose one category according to your forte and start ruling. </p>'),(11699,287,'_about_us_information','field_5f0506be916cb'),(11700,287,'about_us',''),(11701,287,'