e_system_score_list_1_title','field_5f05002e95c4c'),(14659,296,'consecutive_score_system_score_list_1_image','85'),(14660,296,'_consecutive_score_system_score_list_1_image','field_5f05003995c4d'),(14661,296,'consecutive_score_system_score_list_1_description','It’s a game where you have to hit the Hamster and save the Bunny to earn scores. There are two factors which form the basis of its scoring & ranking system. The first one is \'Performance Score\', which means scores are calculated according to the performance of knowledge and/or skill. The second one is \'Time Count\', which means the time taken to complete that particular contest. After calculating both the factors, the final rank is calculated. '),(14662,296,'_consecutive_score_system_score_list_1_description','field_5f05004095c4e'),(14663,296,'consecutive_score_system_score_list_1_link','scoring-ranking-system'),(14664,296,'_consecutive_score_system_score_list_1_link','field_5f05005095c4f'),(14665,296,'consecutive_score_system_score_list_2_title','FLYING BIRD'),(14666,296,'_consecutive_score_system_score_list_2_title','field_5f05002e95c4c'),(14667,296,'consecutive_score_system_score_list_2_image','85'),(14668,296,'_consecutive_score_system_score_list_2_image','field_5f05003995c4d'),(14669,296,'consecutive_score_system_score_list_2_description','It’s a game where if the bird hits the blue balls, you get scores and if the bird hits the black balls, your scores get deducted. There are two factors which form the basis of its scoring & ranking system. The first one is \'Performance Score\', which means scores are calculated according to the performance of knowledge and/or skill. The second one is \'Time Count\', which means the time taken to complete that particular contest. After calculating both the factors, the final rank is calculated.'),(14670,296,'_consecutive_score_system_score_list_2_description','field_5f05004095c4e'),(14671,296,'consecutive_score_system_score_list_2_link','scoring-ranking-system'),(14672,296,'_consecutive_score_system_score_list_2_link','field_5f05005095c4f'),(14673,296,'consecutive_score_system_score_list_3_title','THE BRICK GAME'),(14674,296,'_consecutive_score_system_score_list_3_title','field_5f05002e95c4c'),(14675,296,'consecutive_score_system_score_list_3_image','85'),(14676,296,'_consecutive_score_system_score_list_3_image','field_5f05003995c4d'),(14677,296,'consecutive_score_system_score_list_3_description','It’s a game where you have to create horizontal/vertical grid lines of bricks to earn scores. There are two factors which form the basis of its scoring & ranking system. The first one is \'Performance Score\', which means scores are calculated according to the performance of knowledge and/or skill. The second one is \'Time Count\', which means the time taken to complete that particular contest. After calculating both the factors, the final rank is calculated.'),(14678,296,'_consecutive_score_system_score_list_3_description','field_5f05004095c4e'),(14679,296,'consecutive_score_system_score_list_3_link',''),(14680,296,'_consecutive_score_system_score_list_3_link','field_5f05005095c4f'),(14681,296,'consecutive_score_system_score_list_4_title','THE TIE SITUATION'),(14682,296,'_consecutive_score_system_score_list_4_title','field_5f05002e95c4c'),(14683,296,'consecutive_score_system_score_list_4_image','85'),(14684,296,'_consecutive_score_system_score_list_4_image','field_5f05003995c4d'),(14685,296,'consecutive_score_system_score_list_4_description','In the case of a tie among some of the players, a total sum of all the rewards of those particular players is computed. After that, the average amount is calculated, and equal amounts of money is distributed among all the respective players.'),(14686,296,'_consecutive_score_system_score_list_4_description','field_5f05004095c4e'),(14687,296,'consecutive_score_system_score_list_4_link',''),(14688,296,'_consecutive_score_system_score_list_4_link','field_5f05005095c4f'),(14689,296,'features_boxes_0_i