ll the quizzes are system generated, and MILLIONTREE doesn\'t manipulate the results.The family of MILLIONTREE only allow genuine users to be a part of its universe.</span></p>'),(14704,296,'_features_boxes_1_information','field_5f05056f0be87'),(14705,296,'features_boxes_2_image','89'),(14706,296,'_features_boxes_2_image','field_5f05054f0be84'),(14707,296,'features_boxes_2_title','FACTORS REFLECTING FAIR PLAY'),(14708,296,'_features_boxes_2_title','field_5f05055c0be85'),(14709,296,'features_boxes_2_description','MILLIONTREE maintains its core values by instilling transparency in services, product function & features.  We foster values of trust and faith in'),(14710,296,'_features_boxes_2_description','field_5f0505670be86'),(14711,296,'features_boxes_2_information','<span id=\"three_dots\">...</span><span id=\"three_more\">every arena. We also believe in being responsible towards our user\'s requirements & society\'s needs at the macro level.</span></p>'),(14712,296,'_features_boxes_2_information','field_5f05056f0be87'),(14713,296,'features_boxes_3_image','90'),(14714,296,'_features_boxes_3_image','field_5f05054f0be84'),(14715,296,'features_boxes_3_title','A FIRM TRUST BASE'),(14716,296,'_features_boxes_3_title','field_5f05055c0be85'),(14717,296,'features_boxes_3_description','We strive to ensure that we only have genuine users playing on MILLIONTREE. To facilitate this, we have put in place strict policies and protocols to check any '),(14718,296,'_features_boxes_3_description','field_5f0505670be86'),(14719,296,'features_boxes_3_information','<span id=\"four_dots\">...</span><span id=\"four_more\">violation of MILLIONTREE fair play. We work with trusted third party payment gateway authentication to ensure safety and security of all the financial transactions. We do not store your credit/debit card details with us. All associations of MILLIONTREE are strictly prohibited from participating in any paid contests on MILLIONTREE. The information of PAN Cards and Bank details shared with MILLIONTREE is only used for the user verification purposes and is never disclosed to any outside parties except Indian Govt. authorized parties for verification purposes. And, we do not allow or promote cash transactions on MILLIONTREE. We are sensitive for your valuable money investment. Thus, we may notify users in case their accrued losses exceed ₹30,000.</span></p>'),(14720,296,'_features_boxes_3_information','field_5f05056f0be87'),(14721,296,'faq_0_question','1.   How do I register?'),(14722,296,'_faq_0_question','field_5f050643af48b'),(14723,296,'faq_0_answer','That’s easy! Log on to the MILLIONTREE app. After you’re through with the registration, you can follow the simple starter guide, which will take you through the simple steps of joining contests to win cash. You can also go through the ‘How to Play’ page of MILLIONTREE.'),(14724,296,'_faq_0_answer','field_5f05064aaf48c'),(14725,296,'faq_1_question','2.   Why can’t I log in to my account?'),(14726,296,'_faq_1_question','field_5f050643af48b'),(14727,296,'faq_1_answer','Please check whether your registered email address and password are entered correctly and try logging in again. If you\'ve forgotten your password, click on \'Forgot Password\', enter your registered email ID and we’ll send you a link to reset your password on it within a few minutes! If you\'ve forgotten your registered email id, reach out to us at Contact Us.'),(14728,296,'_faq_1_answer','field_5f05064aaf48c'),(14729,296,'faq_2_question','3.   How many accounts can I create with the same user credentials or the same PAN details?'),(14730,296,'_faq_2_question','field_5f050643af48b'),(14731,296,'faq_2_answer','You can create only one account with one email id on MILLIONTREE. Creation of multiple accounts by a single gamer is strictly prohibited and violates our Fair Play policy.'),(14732,296,'_faq_2_answer','field_5f05064aaf48c'),(14733,296,'faq_3_question','4. What if my internet connection is lost when I am playing the contest?'),(14734,296,'_faq_3_question','field_5f050643af48b'),(14735,296,'faq_3_answer','Once you have confirmed and entered any contest, it is not possible to go backward. Users shall be responsible for any disconnection issues / low bandwidth of internet connection / mobile handset issues, or any other network-related issues that deter the seamless data transfer of MILLIONTREE application. We suggest you maintain a good bandwidth and internet speed while playing MILLIONTREE application.'),(14736,296,'_faq_3_answer','field_5f05064aaf48c'),(14737,296,'faq_4_question','5. What happens if I have bought the ticket, but I was unable to complete the contest before the contest time runs out?'),(14738,296,'_faq_4_question','field_5f050643af48b'),(14739,296,'faq_4_answer','MILLIONTREE does not allow their users to buy ticket for a contest within the last 3 minutes before the contest ends. However, if you have purchased the ticket anytime before the last 3 minutes, you can play the contest till the last second of the available contest time. If the user has bought the ticket but fails to complete the contest before the last second of available contest time, it shall be the sole responsibility of the user to complete the contest within given time, and MILLIONTREE shall not be responsible for the                         same.'),(14740,296,'_faq_4_answer','field_5f05064aaf48c'),(14741,296,'faq_5_question','6. Does the amount in my Winnings Account have any expiry date?'),(14742,296,'_faq_5_question','field_5f050643af48b'),(14743,296,'faq_5_answer','If the amount in your Winnings Account is not withdrawn to your bank account within 335 days from the date of credit, it will be deposited automatically to your bank account, which is on record, provided that your MILLIONTREE account is verified. In case no bank account is provided, or you have failed to complete the verification for the MILLIONTREE account, the amount would stand forfeited. Hence it\'s important that you get your MILLIONTREE account verified as soon as possible.'),(14744,296,'_faq_5_answer','field_5f05064aaf48c'),(14745,296,'faq_6_question','7.   How do I withdraw?'),(14746,296,'_faq_6_question','field_5f050643af48b'),(14747,296,'faq_6_answer','You may withdraw your earnings in the following manner :                          Main page > Left navigation > Menu > Wallet > Withdraw                         You shall be able to withdraw once you have verified the below details:<br>                         1) Mobile and Email Id <br>                         2) PAN details<br>                         3) Bank account details'),(14748,296,'_faq_6_answer','field_5f05064aaf48c'),(14749,296,'faq_7_question','8. Is there any Daily Withdrawal limit?'),(14750,296,'_faq_7_question','field_5f050643af48b'),(14751,296,'faq_7_answer','Yes, you can request a maximum of 3 withdrawals per day and not exceed a total value of Rs.2,00,000/-. The withdrawal amount limit is min. of Rs.200 and max. of Rs.2,00,000 at a time.'),(14752,296,'_faq_7_answer','field_5f05064aaf48c'),(14753,296,'faq_8_question','9. Am I allowed to play if I’m under the age of 18?'),(14754,296,'_faq_8_question','field_5f050643af48b'),(14755,296,'faq_8_answer','No, MILLIONTREE is strictly for users who are at least 18 years of age.'),(14756,296,'_faq_8_answer','field_5f05064aaf48c'),(14757,296,'faq_9_question','10. Is the ticket cost inclusive of all taxes?'),(14758,296,'_faq_9_question','field_5f050643af48b'),(14759,296,'faq_9_answer','The ticket cost as displayed in MILLIONTREE application is inclusive of all the taxes and the player does not need to pay anything besides the ticket costs. So, you do not have to pay additional taxes.'),(14760,296,'_faq_9_answer','field_5f05064aaf48c'),(14761,296,'faq_10_question','11. I do not understand the scoring system. Can you give me some example for a clear understanding?'),(14762,296,'_faq_10_question','field_5f050643af48b'),(14763,296,'faq_10_answer','Sure! Please have a look at the following example:                         If player A answers 4 out of 5 questions correctly in 40 sec,                         If player B answers 5 out of 5 questions correctly in 80 sec,                         and player C answers 2 out of 5 questions correctly in 40 sec.<br>                         The ranking shall be allotted as: Player B – Rank 1, Player A - Rank 2 & Player C - Rank 3.'),(14764,296,'_faq_10_answer','field_5f05064aaf48c'),(14765,296,'faq_11_question','12. Can residents of Assam, Odisha, Telangana, Nagaland and Sikkim participate in paid contests of MILLIONTREE ?'),(14766,296,'_faq_11_question','field_5f050643af48b'),(14767,296,'faq_11_answer','Currently, the residents of Assam, Odisha, Telangana, Nagaland and Sikkim are not permitted to play pay-to-play formats of any online games. The laws in these states are unclear as to whether games of skill may be played for a fee.'),(14768,296,'_faq_11_answer','field_5f05064aaf48c'),(14769,296,'about_us_feature_list_0_icon','91'),(14770,296,'_about_us_feature_list_0_icon','field_5f0506a1916c9'),(14771,296,'about_us_feature_list_0_title','Trust'),(14772,296,'_about_us_feature_list_0_title','field_5f0506a9916ca'),(14773,296,'about_us_feature_list_1_icon','280'),(14774,296,'_about_us_feature_list_1_icon','field_5f0506a1916c9'),(14775,296,'about_us_feature_list_1_title','Ethics'),(14776,296,'_about_us_feature_list_1_title','field_5f0506a9916ca'),(14777,296,'about_us_feature_list_2_icon','93'),(14778,296,'_about_us_feature_list_2_icon','field_5f0506a1916c9'),(14779,296,'about_us_feature_list_2_title','Society & Environment'),(14780,296,'_about_us_feature_list_2_title','field_5f0506a9916ca'),(14781,296,'about_us_feature_list_3_icon','94'),(14782,296,'_about_us_feature_list_3_icon','field_5f0506a1916c9'),(14783,296,'about_us_feature_list_3_title','To Serve'),(14784,296,'_about_us_feature_list_3_title','field_5f0506a9916ca'),(14785,296,'about_us_feature_list_4_icon','95'),(14786,296,'_about_us_feature_list_4_icon','fi