ions_0_title','field_5f0848125ae84'),(15744,312,'questions_0_description','That’s easy! Log on to the MILLIONTREE app. After you’re through with the registration, you can follow the simple starter guide, which will take you through the simple steps of joining contests to win cash. You can also go through the ‘How to Play’ page of MILLIONTREE.'),(15745,312,'_questions_0_description','field_5f0848175ae85'),(15746,312,'questions_1_title','•  How to join a contest after locking your choice?'),(15747,312,'_questions_1_title','field_5f0848125ae84'),(15748,312,'questions_1_description','Join any MILLIONTREE contest shown from the LIVE section by tapping the ‘Join’ button. Thereafter, pay a nominal ticket cost either through your Milliontree wallet or online banking method to confirm your participation. These steps will lead you to the fun part of the contest, i.e., the actual game.'),(15749,312,'_questions_1_description','field_5f0848175ae85'),(15750,312,'questions_2_title','•  How can you finally begin the contest?'),(15751,312,'_questions_2_title','field_5f0848125ae84'),(15752,312,'questions_2_description','Once you join the contest, press the ‘Play’ button to make way for your winning prize so that the glory can be yours! Also, you can flaunt your brilliance by showcasing your improvement in the contests'),(15753,312,'_questions_2_description','field_5f0848175ae85'),(15754,312,'questions_3_title','•  How to spare a glance at your scores after the competition?'),(15755,312,'_questions_3_title','field_5f0848125ae84'),(15756,312,'questions_3_description','In the case of Quiz, Crossword, or Cricbuster, as soon as you finish the contest, you will be able to see your performance scorecard. This scorecard will be displaying the no. of correct answers & the time taken for that particular contest. You can also view the correct answers by simply clicking the ‘View Answers’ tab.</p> 					<p class=\"desc\">Once the contest deadline time is over, rankings shall be declared, and you 