game_steps_3_game_step_number','field_5f084752d9241'),(18197,333,'game_steps_3_image','157'),(18198,333,'_game_steps_3_image','field_5f084776d9242'),(18199,333,'game_steps_3_title','View your performance'),(18200,333,'_game_steps_3_title','field_5f0847e0d9243'),(18201,333,'game_steps_3_description','In the case of Quiz, Crossword or Cricbuster, as soon as you finish the contest you will be able to see your performance scorecard. This scorecard will be displaying the no. of correct answers & the time taken for that particular contest. You can also view the correct answers by simply clicking the ‘View Answers’ tab.<br>  							Once the contest deadline time is over, rankings shall be declared and you will be able to view your rank. Along with it, you can also see the rankings & performance of other participants in the terms of correct answers & time taken, but this happens only after the results are declared.'),(18202,333,'_game_steps_3_description','field_5f0847e6d9244'),(18203,333,'game_steps_4_game_step_number','<span>Step</span><br>05'),(18204,333,'_game_steps_4_game_step_number','field_5f084752d9241'),(18205,333,'game_steps_4_image','158'),(18206,333,'_game_steps_4_image','field_5f084776d9242'),(18207,333,'game_steps_4_title','Withdraw your rewards'),(18208,333,'_game_steps_4_title','field_5f0847e0d9243'),(18209,333,'game_steps_4_description','Withdraw your winnings from your MILLIONTREE account after PAN verification by MILLIONTREE. You can view, withdraw or deposit money into your Milliontree account anytime by clicking the “My Balance” link in the wallet section.<br> 							You will need to go through a One Time Account Verification process before you withdraw any money from your Milliontree account. Don’t worry, this process won’t take time and will not be repeated unless you change any of your details.</p>'),(18210,333,'_game_steps_4_description','field_5f0847e6d9244'),(18211,333,'game_steps_5_game_step_number','<span>Step</span><br>06'),(18212,333,'_game_steps_5_game_step_number','field_5f084752d9241'),(18213,333,'game_steps_5_image','159'),(18214,333,'_game_steps_5_image','field_5f084776d9242'),(18215,333,'game_steps_5_title','View Upcoming contest'),(18216,333,'_game_steps_5_title','field_5f0847e0d9243'),(18217,333,'game_steps_5_description','In the case of Quiz, Crossword or Cricbuster, as soon as you finish the contest you will be able to see your performance scorecard. This scorecard will be displaying the no. of correct answers & the time taken for that particular contest. You can also view the correct answers by simply clicking the ‘View Answers’ tab.<br>  							Once the contest deadline time is over, rankings shall be declared and you will be able to view your rank. Along with it, you can also see the rankings & performance of other participants in the terms of correct answers & time taken, but this happens only after the results are declared.'),(18218,333,'_game_steps_5_description','field_5f0847e6d9244'),(18219,333,'game_steps','6'),(18220,333,'_game_steps','field_5f08474ad9240'),(18221,333,'questions_0_title','•  What should be your first step towards the big goal?'),(18222,333,'_questions_0_title','field_5f0848125ae84'),(18223,333,'questions_0_description','That’s easy! Log on to the MILLIONTREE app. After you’re through with the registration, you can follow the simple starter guide, which will take you through the simple steps of joining contests to win cash. You can also go through the ‘How to Play’ page of MILLIONTREE.'),(18224,333,'_questions_0_description','field_5f0848175ae85'),(18225,333,'questions_1_title','•  How to join a contest after locking your choice?'),(18226,333,'_questions_1_title','field_5f0848125ae84'),(18227,333,'questions_1_description','Join any MILLIONTREE contest shown from the LIVE section by tapping the ‘Join’ button. Thereafter, pay a nominal ticket cost either through your Milliontree wallet or online banking method to confirm your participation. These steps will lead you to the fun part of the contest, i.e., the actual game.'),(18228,333,'_questions_1_description','field_5f0848175ae85'),(18229,333,'questions_2_title','•  How can you finally begin the contest?'),(18230,333,'_questions_2_title','field_5f0848125ae84'),(18231,333,'questions_2_description','Once you join the contest, press the ‘Play’ button to make way for your winning prize so that the glory can be yours! Also, you can flaunt your brilliance by showcasing your improvement in the contests'),(18232,333,'_questions_2_description','field_5f0848175ae85'),(18233,333,'questions_3_title','•  How to spare a glance at your scores after the competition?'),(18234,333,'_questions_3_title','field_5f0848125ae84'),(18235,333,'questions_3_description','In the case of Quiz, Crossword, or Cricbuster, as soon as you finish the contest, you will be able to see your performance scorecard. This scorecard will be displaying the no. of correct answers & the time taken for that particular contest. You can also view the correct answers by simply clicking the ‘View Answers’ tab.</p> 					<p class=\"desc\">Once the contest deadline time is over, rankings shall be declared, and you will be able to view your rank. Along with it, you can also see the rankings & performance of other participants in terms of correct answers & time taken, but this happens only after the results are declared. So, always make it a point to look at the scorecard as this will help you brace yourself for the next challenge!</p>'),(18236,333,'_questions_3_description','field_5f0848175ae85'),(18237,333,'questions_4_title','•  How can you withdraw your hard-earned money after the tournament?'),(18238,333,'_questions_4_title','field_5f0848125ae84'),(18239,333,'questions_4_description','Withdraw your winnings from your MILLIONTREE account after PAN verification by MILLIONTREE. You can view, withdraw, or deposit money into your Milliontree account anytime by clicking the “My Balance” link in the wallet section.</p> 					<p class=\"desc\">You will need to go through a One Time Account Verification process before you withdraw any money from your Milliontree account. Don’t worry; this process won’t take time and will not be repeated unless you change any of your details. So, now you know where to head for your cash!'),(18240,333,'_questions_4_description','field_5f0848175ae85'),(18241,333,'questions_5_title','•  How will you hunt down your next game?'),(18242,333,'_questions_5_title','field_5f0848125ae84'),(18243,333,'questions_5_description','You can see the upcoming contests in the ‘Upcoming’ section for each category and get ready for the next challenge. Ergo, have your shield on always because you never know when it would be the time to hit the game!'),(18244,333,'_questions_5_description','field_5f0848175ae85'),(18245,333,'questions','6'),(18246,333,'_questions','field_5f0848075ae83'),(18357,341,'_edit_lock','1596624273:1'),(18358,341,'_wp_page_template','scoring-ranking-system.php'),(18359,341,'_edit_last','1'),(18360,341,'description','<p class=\"title\">The scoring and ranking system is based on two factors.</p>  	        <p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">a) PERFORMANCE  SCORE: The score achieved purely due to the performance of knowledge and/or skill.</p><br> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">b) TIME COUNT: The amount of time taken to complete that particular contest. The time shall be measured in terms of milliseconds, i.e., represented as  XX:YY:ZZZ (where \'X\' is minutes, and \'Y\' is seconds, and \'Z\' is millisecond). There will be no embedded time limit for this; however, the player has to take care to complete the game within the window time of the contest.</p><br> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">After calculating both the factors, the FINAL RANK shall be calculated.</p><br> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">The FINAL RANK  shall be a combination of (a) and (b), where (a) being the value of knowledge and/or skill shall hold more value than (b). </p>'),(18361,341,'_description','field_5f0836ea4b2cb'),(18362,341,'scenario_table_0_scenario_count','SCENARIO 1'),(18363,341,'_scenario_table_0_scenario_count','field_5f08376b02e0a'),(18364,341,'scenario_table_0_table_heading_0_th_name',''),(18365,341,'_scenario_table_0_table_heading_0_th_name','field_5f0837a902e0c'),(18366,341,'scenario_table_0_table_heading_1_th_name','Player 1'),(18367,341,'_scenario_table_0_table_heading_1_th_name','field_5f0837a902e0c'),(18368,341,'scenario_table_0_table_heading_2_th_name','Player 2'),(18369,341,'_scenario_table_0_table_heading_2_th_name','field_5f0837a902e0c'),(18370,341,'scenario_table_0_table_heading_3_th_name','Player 3'),(18371,341,'_scenario_table_0_table_heading_3_th_name','field_5f0837a902e0c'),(18372,341,'scenario_table_0_table_heading','4'),(18373,341,'_scenario_table_0_table_heading','field_5f08378802e0b'),(18374,341,'scenario_table_0_table_row_0_tr_data',''),(18375,341,'_scenario_table_0_table_row_0_tr_data','field_5f0837db02e0e'),(18376,341,'scenario_table_0_table_row','1'),(18377,341,'_scenario_table_0_table_row','field_5f0837cd02e0d'),(18378,341,'scenario_table','1'),(18379,341,'_scenario_table','field_5f08372802e09'),(18380,341,'table_0_table_heading_0_th_data',''),(18381,341,'_table_0_table_heading_0_th_data','field_5f0bfe21b192f'),(18382,341,'table_0_table_heading_1_th_data','Player 1'),(18383,341,'_table_0_table_heading_1_th_data','field_5f0bfe21b192f'),(18384,341,'table_0_table_heading_2_th_data','Player 2'),(18385,341,'_table_0_table_heading_2_th_data','field_5f0bfe21b192f'),(18386,341,'table_0_table_heading','4'),(18387,341,'_table_0_table_heading','field_5f0bfdefb192e'),(18388,341,'table_0_table_row_0_tr_data',''),(18389,341,'_table_0_table_row_0_tr_data','field_5f083b078c177'),(18390,341,'table_0_table_row','1'),(18391,341,'_table_0_table_row','field_5f083af88c176'),(18392,341,'table','3'),(18393,341,'_t