ny_description','<h2 class=\"main_heading\">RANKING & SCORING Method FOR<br> ‘HIT THE HAMSTER - SAVE THE BUNNY’</h2> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">It’s a game where you have to hit the Hamster and save the Bunny to earn scores. Also remember, sometimes you can also spot Double Hamsters. </p> 			<p class=\"title\">The FINAL RANKING of every contest for all the users is based on two parameters:  </p> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">a) PERFORMANCE  SCORE: The score achieved purely due to the performance of knowledge and/or skill.</p><br> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">b) TIME COUNT: The amount of time taken to complete that particular contest. The time shall be measured in terms of milliseconds, i.e., represented as  XX:YY:ZZZ (where \'X\' is minutes, and \'Y\' is seconds, and \'Z\' is millisecond). 			There will be no embedded time limit for this; however, the player has to take care to complete the game within the window time of the contest.</p><br> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">After calculating both the factors, the FINAL RANK shall be calculated.</p><br> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">The FINAL RANK  shall be a combination of (a) and (b), where (a) being the value of knowledge and/or skill shall hold more value than (b). </p> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">The user shall get a chance to play the game 3 times on one ticket, and the average of all the 3 PERFORMANCE SCORES shall be considered for all the players.</p>'),(18541,341,'_save_the_bunny_description','field_5f0c17ff287a0'),(18542,341,'bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_one',''),(18543,341,'_bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_one','field_5f0c184d402e5'),(18544,341,'bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_two',''),(18545,341,'_bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_two','field_5f0ec2adc2b94'),(18546,341,'bunny_table_data_0_tr