"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">b) TIME COUNT: The amount of time taken to complete that particular contest. The time shall be measured in terms of milliseconds, i.e., represented as  XX:YY:ZZZ (where \'X\' is minutes, and \'Y\' is seconds, and \'Z\' is millisecond). 			There will be no embedded time limit for this; however, the player has to take care to complete the game within the window time of the contest.</p><br> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">After calculating both the factors, the FINAL RANK shall be calculated.</p><br> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">The FINAL RANK  shall be a combination of (a) and (b), where (a) being the value of knowledge and/or skill shall hold more value than (b). </p> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">The user shall get a chance to play the game 3 times on one ticket, and the average of all the 3 PERFORMANCE SCORES shall be considered for all the players.</p>'),(20274,342,'_save_the_bunny_description','field_5f0c17ff287a0'),(20275,342,'bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_one',''),(20276,342,'_bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_one','field_5f0c184d402e5'),(20277,342,'bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_two',''),(20278,342,'_bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_two','field_5f0ec2adc2b94'),(20279,342,'bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_three',''),(20280,342,'_bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_three','field_5f0ec2bbc2b97'),(20281,342,'bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_one',''),(20282,342,'_bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_one','field_5f0c184d402e5'),(20283,342,'bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_two',''),(20284,342,'_bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_two','field_5f0ec2adc2b94'),(20285,342,'bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_three',''),(20286,342,'_bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_three','field_5f0ec2bbc2b97'),(20287,342,'bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_one',''),(20288,342,'_bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_one','field_5f0c184d402e5'),(20289,342,'bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_two',''),(20290,342,'_bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_two',