e window time of the contest.</p><br> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">After calculating both the factors, the FINAL RANK shall be calculated.</p><br> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">The FINAL RANK  shall be a combination of (a) and (b), where (a) being the value of knowledge and/or skill shall hold more value than (b). </p> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">The user shall get a chance to play the game 3 times on one ticket, and the average of all the 3 PERFORMANCE SCORES shall be considered for all the players.</p>'),(22946,408,'_save_the_bunny_description','field_5f0c17ff287a0'),(22947,408,'bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_one',''),(22948,408,'_bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_one','field_5f0c184d402e5'),(22949,408,'bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_two',''),(22950,408,'_bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_two','field_5f0ec2adc2b94'),(22951,408,'bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_three',''),(22952,408,'_bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_three','field_5f0ec2bbc2b97'),(22953,408,'bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_one',''),(22954,408,'_bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_one','field_5f0c184d402e5'),(22955,408,'bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_two',''),(22956,408,'_bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_two','field_5f0ec2adc2b94'),(22957,408,'bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_three',''),(22958,408,'_bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_three','field_5f0ec2bbc2b97'),(22959,408,'bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_one',''),(22960,408,'_bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_one','field_5f0c184d402e5'),(22961,408,'bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_two',''),(22962,408,'_bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_two','field_5f0ec2adc2b94'),(22963,408,'bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_three',''),(22964,408,'_bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_three','field_5f0ec2bbc2b97'),(22965,408,'bunny_table_data_3_tr_data_one',''),(22966,408,'_bunny_table_data_3_tr_data_one','field_5f0c184d402e5'),(22967,408,'bunny_table_data_3_tr_data_two',''),(22968,408,'_bunny_table_data_3_tr_data_two','field_5f0ec2adc2b94'),(22969,408,'bunn