ll the users is based on two parameters:  </p> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">a) PERFORMANCE  SCORE: The score achieved purely due to the performance of knowledge and/or skill.</p><br> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">b) TIME COUNT: The amount of time taken to complete that particular contest. The time shall be measured in terms of milliseconds, i.e., represented as  XX:YY:ZZZ (where \'X\' is minutes, and \'Y\' is seconds, and \'Z\' is millisecond). 			There will be no embedded time limit for this; however, the player has to take care to complete the game within the window time of the contest.</p><br> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">After calculating both the factors, the FINAL RANK shall be calculated.</p><br> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">The FINAL RANK  shall be a combination of (a) and (b), where (a) being the value of knowledge and/or skill shall hold more value than (b). </p> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">The user shall get a chance to play the game 3 times on one ticket, and the average of all the 3 PERFORMANCE SCORES shall be considered for all the players.</p>'),(23663,409,'_save_the_bunny_description','field_5f0c17ff287a0'),(23664,409,'bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_one',''),(23665,409,'_bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_one','field_5f0c184d402e5'),(23666,409,'bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_two',''),(23667,409,'_bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_two','field_5f0ec2adc2b94'),(23668,409,'bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_three',''),(23669,409,'_bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_three','field_5f0ec2bbc2b97'),(23670,409,'bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_one',''),(23671,409,'_bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_one','field_5f0c184d402e5'),(23672,409,'bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_two',''),(23673,409,'_bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_two','field_5f0ec2adc2b94'),(23674,409,'bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_three',''),(23675,409,'_bunny_table_