 seconds, and \'Z\' is millisecond). 			There will be no embedded time limit for this; however, the player has to take care to complete the game within the window time of the contest.</p><br> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">After calculating both the factors, the FINAL RANK shall be calculated.</p><br> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">The FINAL RANK  shall be a combination of (a) and (b), where (a) being the value of knowledge and/or skill shall hold more value than (b). </p> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">The user shall get a chance to play the game 3 times on one ticket, and the average of all the 3 PERFORMANCE SCORES shall be considered for all the players.</p>'),(25928,412,'_save_the_bunny_description','field_5f0c17ff287a0'),(25929,412,'bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_one',''),(25930,412,'_bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_one','field_5f0c184d402e5'),(25931,412,'bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_two',''),(25932,412,'_bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_two','field_5f0ec2adc2b94'),(25933,412,'bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_three',''),(25934,412,'_bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_three','field_5f0ec2bbc2b97'),(25935,412,'bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_one',''),(25936,412,'_bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_one','field_5f0c184d402e5'),(25937,412,'bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_two',''),(25938,412,'_bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_two','field_5f0ec2adc2b94'),(25939,412,'bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_three',''),(25940,412,'_bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_three','field_5f0ec2bbc2b97'),(25941,412,'bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_one',''),(25942,412,'_bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_one','field_5f0c184d402e5'),(25943,412,'bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_two',''),(25944,412,'_bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_two','field_5f0ec2adc2b94'),(25945,412,'bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_three',''),(25946,412,'_bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_three','field_5f0ec2bbc2b97'),(25947,412,'bunny_table_data_3_tr_data_one',''),(25948,412,'_bunny_table_data_3_tr_data_one','