NCE  SCORE: The score achieved purely due to the performance of knowledge and/or skill.</p><br> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">b) TIME COUNT: The amount of time taken to complete that particular contest. The time shall be measured in terms of milliseconds, i.e., represented as  XX:YY:ZZZ (where \'X\' is minutes, and \'Y\' is seconds, and \'Z\' is millisecond). 			There will be no embedded time limit for this; however, the player has to take care to complete the game within the window time of the contest.</p><br> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">After calculating both the factors, the FINAL RANK shall be calculated.</p><br> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">The FINAL RANK  shall be a combination of (a) and (b), where (a) being the value of knowledge and/or skill shall hold more value than (b). </p> 			<p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">The user shall get a chance to play the game 3 times on one ticket, and the average of all the 3 PERFORMANCE SCORES shall be considered for all the players.</p>'),(27438,414,'_save_the_bunny_description','field_5f0c17ff287a0'),(27439,414,'bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_one',''),(27440,414,'_bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_one','field_5f0c184d402e5'),(27441,414,'bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_two',''),(27442,414,'_bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_two','field_5f0ec2adc2b94'),(27443,414,'bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_three',''),(27444,414,'_bunny_table_data_0_tr_data_three','field_5f0ec2bbc2b97'),(27445,414,'bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_one',''),(27446,414,'_bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_one','field_5f0c184d402e5'),(27447,414,'bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_two',''),(27448,414,'_bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_two','field_5f0ec2adc2b94'),(27449,414,'bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_three',''),(27450,414,'_bunny_table_data_1_tr_data_three','field_5f0ec2bbc2b97'),(27451,414,'bunny_table_data_2_tr_data_one',''),(27452,414,'_bunny_table_data_2_tr