,458,'_about_us_feature_list','field_5f050698916c8'),(30556,458,'about_us_information','We strongly believe that we should also contribute to the societal goals for the overall betterment of the nation. This notion has inspired us to do our bit for the welfare of farmers and Indian defense forces in the form of our CSR activities. </p>         <p class=\"desc\" data-aos=\"fade-up\" data-aos-duration=\"2000\">All in all now is the time for you to grab the golden chance to win prizes at minimal prices. Just choose one category according to your forte and start ruling. </p>'),(30557,458,'_about_us_information','field_5f0506be916cb'),(30558,458,'about_us',''),(30559,458,'_about_us','field_5f05067b916c6'),(30560,458,'banner_slider_1_image','327'),(30561,458,'_banner_slider_1_image','field_5f04fc666fad3'),(30562,458,'banner_slider_2_image','330'),(30563,458,'_banner_slider_2_image','field_5f04fc666fad3'),(30564,458,'mobile_banner','3'),(30565,458,'_mobile_banner','field_5f050dcfa08e8'),(30566,458,'zone_0_name','QUIZ'),(30567,458,'_zone_0_name','field_5f04fe5271001'),(30568,458,'zone_0_description','Let your gray matter do some work as this zone is based on 100% knowledge and nothing else. And, it\'s a golden chance for you to relive your childhood as you are going to get a nostalgic hit. Presenting the four segments of this zone:'),(30569,458,'_zone_0_description','field_5f04fe6171002'),(30570,458,'zone_0_list','4'),(30571,458,'_zone_0_list','field_5f04fe8271004'),(30572,458,'zone_0_image','75'),(30573,458,'_zone_0_image','field_5f04fe7071003'),(30574,458,'banner_slider_0_title_one',''),(30575,458,'_banner_slider_0_title_one','field_5f050db179638'),(30576,458,'banner_slider_0_title_two',''),(30577,458,'_banner_slider_0_title_two','field_5f050dc279639'),(30578,458,'banner_slider_1_title_one',''),(30579,458,'_banner_slider_1_title_one','field_5f050db179638'),(30580,458,'banner_slider_1_title_two',''),(30581,458,'_banner_slider_1_title_two','field_5f050dc279639'),(30582,458,