 in the contest getting displayed on the LIVE section. The sooner you will finish the contest, the higher will be your chances of winning. For zones like Quiz, Crosswords and Crickbuster, your ranking is based on no. of correct answers and the time taken by you to complete the contest. While for the Games category, your ranking is based on the maximum score you have obtained in given time.'),(30853,460,'_how_to_play_description','field_5f04fecdf42f2'),(30854,460,'how_to_play_image','83'),(30855,460,'_how_to_play_image','field_5f04fef2f42f3'),(30856,460,'how_to_play_steps','6'),(30857,460,'_how_to_play_steps','field_5f04ff1af42f4'),(30858,460,'how_to_play',''),(30859,460,'_how_to_play','field_5f04fec1f42f1'),(30860,460,'consecutive_score_system_description','There are two factors which form the basis of the entire scoring & ranking system. The first one is \'Performance Score\', which means scores are calculated according to the performance of knowledge and/or skill. The second one is \'Time Count\', which means the time taken to complete that particular contest. After calculating both the factors, the final rank is calculated.'),(30861,460,'_consecutive_score_system_description','field_5f04fffe95c4a'),(30862,460,'consecutive_score_system_score_list','5'),(30863,460,'_consecutive_score_system_score_list','field_5f05002495c4b'),(30864,460,'consecutive_score_system',''),(30865,460,'_consecutive_score_system','field_5f04fff195c49'),(30866,460,'features_description','An app is always defined by its features and specifics. MILLIONTREE has four basic peculiarities which make it unique. These characteristics are portrayed by our provision of equality to all the players, reflection of transparency, availability of fair play and a firm trust base. '),(30867,460,'_features_description','field_5f0500920be82'),(30868,460,'features_boxes','4'),(30869,460,'_features_boxes','field_5f0500d60be83'),(30870,460,'features',''),(30871,460,'_features','field_5f0500810be81'),(30872,460,'fa